				<wikidot:authorName>MaliceAforethought</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I read it as the scip being what we consider &quot;normality&quot;, and that the Researcher's the only person left who's still human. Everyone else has had their brains shut down, creating the inactive areas, and this guy's the one person who can still act in the normal, appropriate way &#8212; hence &quot;everybody else&quot;.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-4130249#post-3624190</guid>
